{"tid":253421,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)關鍵密碼 猛火爆1-2","createTime":"2017-05-22T11:34:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-22T17:00:20.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f92d7bfce462c533e48be52b8eacdd95e19cbbd","tid":253421,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:34:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2F&d=aISpdGVq1OuJ%2BcpSKkhvRcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=c42d19cd\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/</a> CC台又執柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=aISpdGVq1OuJ%2BcpSKkhvRcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=b308b5a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a>可以直接睇到V台<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=aISpdGVq1OuJ%2BcpSKkhvRcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=de33ae3a\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"http://pic.pimg.tw/monkey1980/49d2f320d71db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.pimg.tw%2Fmonkey1980%2F49d2f320d71db.jpg&h=42ec5552&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/c/c4/猛火爆.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Fc%2Fc4%2F%E7%8C%9B%E7%81%AB%E7%88%86.jpg&h=652b211c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/9/9e/RED_2_poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F9%2F9e%2FRED_2_poster.jpg&h=fa1b39df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.史萊文(喬許哈奈特) 借住在朋友尼克的公寓，沒想到尼克卻因為積欠「老闆」的錢，偷偷先落跑了&hellip;。<br />\n債主「老闆」是紐約兩大地下勢力之一的頭頭，他和另一惡勢力的首腦「拉比」倆人為敵已久。「老闆」想暗殺「拉比」的兒子洩恨，於是命令手下去找尼克，逼他執行這個任務來抵債&hellip;。<br />\n<br />\n2.法蘭克莫西斯（Frank Moses；布魯斯&middot;威利飾演）是一名自CIA退休的前特工，被CIA的分類為RED，即為已退休而極度危險的（Retired, Extremely Dangerous），他感到退休生活十分無趣沒有變化，唯一的樂趣是每月撕毀養老金支票藉故與養老金管理人莎拉羅斯（Sarah Ross；瑪莉&middot;露易絲&middot;派克飾演）在電話裡的談天說地時間，且法蘭克對莎拉在心中漸生情愫；一日法蘭克家中突然闖入了數名傭兵，想要將法蘭克滅口，法蘭克憑著過去的矯健身手將傭兵團擊退後，發現攻擊的背後有著巨大的陰謀存在；因此為了保護所愛的人，法蘭克決定召集過去的老戰友們，來對抗陰謀的幕後黑手並揭發真相&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n3.出生入死、爾虞我詐的諜報世界裡，你要相信薑是老的辣！退而不休，寶刀未老的探員法蘭克（布魯斯威利 飾）憑著往昔經驗和過人能耐，將與他的昔日戰友再度出手，不但要拯救世界免於核子威脅，更要保全他們自己的老命...<br />\n<br />\n8 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7b18a2fa487c169e5aa09e1b28a269fe46f7d4","tid":253421,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T11:37:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5724ec39a57a668fdb5abb6a43ce8bb73ab9f73d","tid":253421,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T12:24:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41063dd8a34238c807efa06f4574607e643d20f5","tid":253421,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e7f2b8642bf578816cfb2e781eaf2ea445070c","tid":253421,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T14:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img sr